nodes.text: The Parapa Cartel was a criminal organization led by the Frizznoth Mozeen Parapa. They tracked the Phylanx Redux Transmitter to Freerago's Satellite Diner and Motel, requesting the assistance of Sana Starros and Han Solo to find it and deliver it to them. However, Starros had planned to hand the device over to the Droid Gotra, resulting in a fight between Gorben Frak and the Parapa Cartel aboard the Millennium Falcon. Frustrated by the dispute, Solo threw the Phylanx out of the starship's trash chute.
